THE APPROACH
We believe the task ahead for Point 97 is to create a well-designed, disruptive product based upon a rock solid business strategy then tell that story to the world. 
But because your organization is neither a pure startup, nor a pure non-profit, we also believe success depends on our finding a careful balance between short term startup needs and the considered thoughtfulness and measured growth that is often the hallmark of work within the non-profit space. 
On the following page we have grouped the tasks associated with each of the deliverables into distinct phases. The discovery phase establishes the foundation for the others, which we see ebbing and flowing over the life cycle of the Point 97 product development.  In total, this approach represents an engagement that can be flexible and pivot as Point 97â€™s needs inevitably change over time.
